abort.invalid_webhook_url:
Safegate Pro is not configured correctly to receive updates from SmartThings. The webhook URL is invalid:
> {webhook_url}

Please update your configuration per the [instructions]({component_url}), restart Safegate Pro, and try again.

user.description:
SmartThings will be configured to send push updates to Safegate Pro at:
> {webhook_url}

If this is not correct, please update your configuration, restart Safegate Pro, and try again.
